---
title: "Wearables + AI + Autoimmune Disease"
excerpt: "Rheumatoid arthritis (RA) flares are unpredictable and often detected only after symptom escalation, delaying treatment adjustments and increasing the risk of joint damage. There is a critical need for continuous, objective monitoring tools that can identify early physiologic signals of disease worsening."
permalink: /projects/ra
